726347f-a.text:
Colonial Averue, east side, in the Horace Hardirg Blvd., showing two views of the Titus house located on the site of the Coe house. Rikers map of Newtown (1852) shows a mill in
this area, but no Coe or Titus house.
1922
Views 1and 2
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
